data.description: Luxurious 4 bed and office, 3 bath, 3 garage home in highly coveted Lake Wellington Estates. Excellent schools. West Foundation elementary in same neighborhood. High ceilings and open concept. Kitchen with granite counters, custom cabinetry & gas cooktop. Formal dining and eat in kitchen. Large isolated master with remodeled master bath and stunning custom tile work. POOL added in 2020 to make yourbackyard an oasis. Storm shelter. 2019 Class 4 roof. Ecobee system. This home has it all. Call ASAP to schedule your tour! Schedule your tour today and offer!
